trpzExternalServerCompliance.description: The compliance statement for devices that implement the External Server MIB. This compliance statement was for releases 6.0 to 7.3 of AC (wireless switch) software. This compliance statement is replaced by trpzExternalServerComplianceRev2.

trpzExternalServerComplianceRev2.name: trpzExternalServerComplianceRev2
trpzExternalServerComplianceRev2.description: The compliance statement for devices that implement the External Server MIB. This compliance statement is for releases 7.5 and greater of AC (wireless switch) software.
